<p>As if on cue, something stirred from behind him. Limbs lazy, almost mindless, like a dismembered octopus tentacle, laying themselves on Judas.</p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p>&quot;Ohhh, him! Well, you know, there was this, this initiate who had him, but that t-tricky rat just&#8230; wormed his way out! Ran towards the center of town, like a coward. Looked almost <em>immune</em> to <tt>BLACK FLY</tt>; he's that much of a degenerate, you know?&quot;</p>
